'''Tree stump''' is a scenery object found on [[Crandor]] near the dungeon entrance. The tree stump appears burnt, and does not respawn into a tree. The tree stump has no interaction options and is purely decorative.

The tree stump is visually identical to one of the unused [[Tree stump (Wilderness)#Unused 1|tree stumps]] likely intended to be used in the burnt portions of the [[Wilderness]], and has the same examine text.
